'''石牆圖書與檔案館'''（{{lang|en|Stonewall Library & Archives}}）是一座位於[[美國|美國]][[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[羅德岱堡|羅德岱堡]]的私立圖書館，致力於收藏和[[女同性戀|女同性戀]]、[[男同性戀|男同性戀]]、[[雙性戀|雙性戀]]與[[跨性別者|跨性別者]]相關的歷史文獻或相關出版品。<ref name=libmission>{{Cite web|url=http://www.stonewall-library.org/mission.html|title=Mission/History|publisher=Stonewall Library & Archives|language=en|accessdate=2007-07-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070730101157/http://stonewall-library.org/mission.html|archivedate=2007-07-30}}</ref>石牆圖書與檔案館有超過18,000件書籍、影片和DVD館藏對外開放閱覽，<ref name=foundabout>{{Cite web|url=http://stonewallfoundation.com/about.html|title=The Pioneer Founders:About Us|publisher=Stonewall Library & Archives Foundation|language=en|accessdate=2007-07-17|archive-date=2007-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070920055735/http://stonewallfoundation.com/about.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[美國東南部|美國東南部]]LGBT文物收藏量最大的圖書館。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/upi/index.php?feed=TopNews&article=UPI-1-20070609-19463700-bc-us-gaylibrary.xml |title=So. Fla. gay library moving |date=9 June 2007 |publisher=[[合眾國際社|合眾國際社]] |language=en |accessdate=2007-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930181215/http://www.sciencedaily.com/upi/index.php?feed=TopNews&article=UPI-1-20070609-19463700-bc-us-gaylibrary.xml |archivedate=2007-09-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=member>{{cite web |url=http://www.stonewall-library.org/getinvolved.html |title=Get Involved |publisher=Stonewall Library & Archives |language=en |accessdate=2007-07-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929143428/http://www.stonewall-library.org/getinvolved.html |archivedate=2007-09-29 }}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
石牆圖書與檔案館成立於1973年，由位於佛羅里達州的石牆委員會所推動設立。首任館長是馬克·西爾伯（{{lang|en|Mark N. Silber}}）。成立初期，圖書館僅開放給特定許可團體參觀，直到1985年5月25日才向外界開放。之後圖書館和博卡拉頓南方男同性戀檔案館（{{lang|en|Boca Raton-based Southern Gay Archives}}）合併，並組成「石牆圖書與檔案館公司」負責管理。2001年，圖書館址遷往安德魯斯大街1717號的南佛羅里達男女同性戀社區中心。<ref name=TFA>{{cite journal |last=Searcy |first=Fred |journal=''The Florida Archivist'' |title=Stonewall Library and Archives Moves into the New Millennium |volume= 17 |issue= 1 |year=2001 |language=en |pages= 2–3}}</ref>

然而，由於社區中心即將拆毀，因此圖書館必須另覓館址。館方在[[布勞沃德縣|布勞沃德縣]][[羅德岱堡|羅德岱堡]]找到由布勞沃德縣立圖書館分館提供場地。2007年6月10日，布勞沃德縣以9-0表決通過允許石牆圖書與檔案館設址於該縣的羅德岱堡市。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/columnists/sfl-flbmayocol19nbjul19,0,4087832.column |title=Fort Lauderdale mayor turning into his own worst enemy |author=Mayo, Michael |publisher=''Sun-Sentinel'' |date=2007-07-19 |language=en |accessdate=2007-07-23 |archive-date=2012-09-14 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120914144028/http://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/columnists/sfl-flbmayocol19nbjul19,0,4087832.column |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/opinion/sfl-forum19librarynbjul19,0,6738018.story |title=New facility offers public local resources |author=Rutland, Jack |publisher=''Sun-Sentinel'' |language=en |date=2007-07-19 |accessdate=2007-07-23 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>新館於2009年2月開放。

2007年7月10日，羅德岱堡市以3-2投票允許石牆圖書與檔案館長期租用一棟市政府所擁有的建築。但在表決前，市長{{Link-en|吉姆·諾格爾|Jim Naugle}}公開指責圖書館收藏有色情資訊。圖書館執行主任傑克·拉特蘭（{{lang|en|Jack Rutland}}）指出，市長所指的那三件收藏都屬於圖書館7,000件非流通藏品之一，收藏僅供保存與研究之用。<ref name=advocate>{{Cite news |url=http://www.advocate.com/news_detail_ektid47327.asp |title=Naugle notwithstanding, Fort Lauderdale to get new LGBT library |author=Wilcox, Barbara |publisher=''The Advocate'' |language=en |date=2007-07-12 |accessdate=2007-07-17 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927194807/http://www.advocate.com/news_detail_ektid47327.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>當地同志社群為此風波和諾格爾發生多起爭執，諾格爾並多次發表反同性戀聲明。

